{"body": {"name": "Eth Samba Hacker House and NEAR day", "summary": "The Hacker House will host Near Campus Students that will be hacking during EthSamba Hackathon. \\\\n\\\\nNear Day is a ecossystem focused event that will prepare hackers to build on Near.", "category": "Universities & Bootcamps", "timeline": {"status": "DRAFT"}, "supervisor": "bpolania.near", "description": "##### Hacker House \\\\n\\\\nThe hacker house will be hosting students from the Universities ITA and Intelli, they are part of Near Campus program and have been onboarded to Near Ecossystem. \\\\n\\\\n*List of names and contacts are available in demand.\\\\n\\\\nCost of the house for 5 nights: $1380\\\\n \\\\n##### Near Day\\\\n\\\\nNear Day is a event pre hackathon that will welcome devs to the near ecossystem, getting prepared to build on the hackathon.\\\\n\\\\nAudio Visual equipaments and food for 50 hackers are included to the price: $1000\\\\n\\\\n##### Swags\\\\n\\\\nProduction of 100 white shirts 6 dollars each + Delivery \\\\n\\\\nTotal $620\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n", "linked_proposals": [], "receiver_account": "8566fc4bb16e1a7446b5e9b1b8aea94b5751d5f8c658d7af18d8cdf642d7b31d", "requested_sponsor": "neardevdao.near", "proposal_body_version": "V0", "requested_sponsorship_usd_amount": "3000", "requested_sponsorship_paid_in_currency": "USDC"}, "labels": []}
